OL,3,COne in two LGBT+ people say they are
OL,4,Cbullied or harassed at work ` survey
OL,6,FOne in two lesbian, gay, bisexual and
OL,7,Ftrans (LGBT+) people say they are
OL,8,Fbeing bullied or harassed at work, new
OL,9,Fresearch suggests.
OL,11,FA survey of 1,000 LGBT+ people by the
OL,12,FTUC indicated that one in five had
OL,13,Fbeen exposed to verbal abuse at work
OL,14,Fin the last five years.
OL,16,FMore than a quarter of respondents
OL,17,Fsaid they had homophobic, biphobic or
OL,18,Ftransphobic remarks directed at them
OL,19,For made in their presence.
