OL,3,COne in two LGBT+ people say they are
OL,4,Cbullied or harassed at work ` survey
OL,6,FOne in 20 told the TUC they had
OL,7,Fexperienced physical violence, threats
OL,8,For intimidation at work because of
OL,9,Ftheir sexual orientation.
OL,11,FThe union organisation said it was not
OL,12,Fsurprising that nearly three in 10
OL,13,FLGBT+ people keep their sexual
OL,14,Forientation a secret at work.
OL,16,FThe survey found that on every
OL,17,Fmeasure, young LGBT+ workers aged
OL,18,Fbetween 18 and 24 are experiencing
OL,19,Fhigher levels of discrimination at
OL,20,Fwork.
