OL,6,FTUC general secretary Paul Nowak said:
OL,7,F"This new report shines a light on the
OL,8,Fextent of discrimination LGBT+ workers
OL,9,Fface in our workplaces.
OL,11,F"LGBT+ people should be safe and
OL,12,Fsupported at work, but instead,
OL,13,Fthey're experiencing shockingly high
OL,14,Flevels of bullying and harassment `
OL,15,Fincluding assault.
